rows.label: qst701509_msg0003
rows.name:
It has been a long time. We
have both aged, haven't we?

rows.label: qst701509_msg0004
rows.name:
Well, well, this is... I'm at
a loss. What a day this is.

rows.label: qst701509_msg0005
rows.name:
Have you created your
"greatest work"? I have
been waiting for it, Mirei.

rows.label: qst701509_msg0007
rows.name:
You surely weren't waiting
for long. Fufu, you're as
bad at lying as ever.

rows.label: qst701509_msg0008
rows.name:
Foffoffo... Your habit of forcing
a laugh when you're trying to hide
something hasn't changed either.

rows.label: qst701509_msg0009
rows.name: In any case, let's talk inside.
